        {
            "_id": "P4udhPlUFL1dXZ9A",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
            "name": "Reef Bond",
            "sort": 800000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Every coral dragon is mystically bound to a single living coral reef. If the dragon moves more than 3 miles from their reef, they become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} and unable to recover, with the sickened value increasing by 1 every 6 hours unless they succeed at a @Check[fortitude|dc:46] save. After 24 hours, the dragon becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1}; their drained value increases by 1 every 24 hours.</p>\n<p>If the dragon's reef suffers significant physical damage, they immediately become aware of the location where the reef was harmed, but not the source or nature of the damage. Should the reef ever be completely destroyed, the dragon is immediately slain.</p>"
                },
